Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.92,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}夢想的盡頭通向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:41.80,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}世界正待我們去探尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:50.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}滿懷真正的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:55.75,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在心的指引下前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:00.57,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}有你陪伴定能去向天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:06.29,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}奔向每個角落 心靈無拘無束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:12.41,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你的微笑讓我領悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:18.22,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我渴求的力量便藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:19.86,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}騰空而起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:25.39,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}定要接近那片光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.51,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}觸及希望燎原的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.02,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}曾經目睹的那個夢想
